node.text: Looks really appetising and feels like a King’s feast! 😅

Actually made plans to visit @TessBarAndKitchen pre-COVID, so I guess today’s lunch delivery makes up for that.
🔸
Definite highlights include their masterfully tender Grilled Lamb Short Ribs, fail-proof Oven-roasted Bone Marrow with Angus beef cubes and Angus Beef Tagliatelle with slow-cooked wagyu beef ragu and poached egg. Order via https://tessbarandkitchen.oddle.me/en_SG/ 😍 #FindNewFood
